ference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/grant\">grant</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of heart \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/heart\">heart</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of incroyable \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/incroyable\">incroyable</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of megalocardia \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/megalocardia\">megalocardia</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of miscreant \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/miscreant\">miscreant</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of myocardium \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/myocardium\">myocardium</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of pericarditis \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/pericarditis\">pericarditis</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of pericardium \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/pericardium\">pericardium</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of quarry \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/quarry#etymonline_v_3150\">quarry</a> (n.1) \"what is hunted; \" <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of record \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/record\">record</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of recreant \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/recreant\">recreant</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of tachycardia \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/tachycardia\">tachycardia</a>。</p><p>它是假设的来源，其存在的证据由以下单词提供：希腊语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kardia</i>，拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cor</i>，亚美尼亚语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">sirt</i>，古爱尔兰语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cride</i>，威尔士语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">craidd</i>，赫梯语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kir</i>，立陶宛语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">širdis</i>，俄语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">serdce</i>，古英语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">heorte</i>，德语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Herz</i>，哥特语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">hairto</i>，“心脏”； 布列塔尼语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kreiz</i>，“中间”； 古教会斯拉夫语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">sreda</i>，“中间”。</p>"
